snippet.title: Diana is Waiting for a Friend, dresses up and does makeup
snippet.description:
While Diana was resting, she got a phone call from Roma. Roma said he wanted to come over. Diana started getting ready for the visit: she cleaned the house, dressed up and even did her makeup! However, when Diana gets ready, Roma calls her again and sais he changed his mind…
